"Der Mailserver liefert ausgehende Mail an den Mailserver "
"``mx01.example.com`` auf Port ``587``."

#: ../../mail/configuration-server.rst:37
msgid ""
":program:`Postfix` determines the actual target address of the relay mail"
" server by querying the MX/SRV record in the DNS. To turn off MX lookup, "
"use the format :samp:`[{FQDN relay host}]`, as you see in the following "
"examples:"
msgstr ""
